<a href="/staff/100276/khai-trung-le/">
<img alt="Khai Trung Le" title="Khai Trung Le" src="https://media.pocketgamer.biz/2022/6/117298/khai-trung-le1-rx145.jpg">
</a>
</div>
<div class="author">
<a class="link" href="/staff/100276/khai-trung-le/">Khai Trung Le</a>
</div>
<div class="author-role">Editor</div>
<p>Former editor of PocketGamer.biz, Khai can also be found on Vice, Star Trek, and in numerous scientific journals and publications.</p>
</div>
